    {
      "item_id": "6b5d66625e:1",
      "translation": "PxrDomeLight",
      "words": [
        "PxrDomeLight"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6b5d66625e:2",
      "translation": "时，daylight simulation（日光模拟）非常有用。它的简单性和真实感让这种灯光成为艺术家的常用选择。",
      "words": [
